16:03.760 --> 16:07.071
Come on, if I do a photo shoot today,
what's tomorrow,

16:07.160 --> 16:09.356
swimsuit competition, talent show?

16:09.440 --> 16:10.440
Okay.

16:10.520 --> 16:12.830
