he is hitting all four of the "E's."

21:47.480 --> 21:48.994
We added an "E"?

21:50.720 --> 21:53.315
<i>Gary Hart, known as
the voice of a new generation,</i>

21:53.400 --> 21:55.960
<i>continues to inspire voters
both young and old,</i>

21:56.040 --> 21:58.316
<i>who say this Colorado senator
has both the presence</i>

21:58.400 --> 22:00.073
<i>and idealism of a Kennedy.</i>

