25:06.640 --> 25:07.994
Nice boat.

25:08.080 --> 25:09.799
- Yeah.
- Right?

25:09.880 --> 25:11.872
<i>Deep in my mind</i>

25:11.960 --> 25:14.794
It's just, I, you know...
