25:17.560 --> 25:20.200
<i>Good times</i>

25:20.360 --> 25:23.432
<i>And faces that remind me</i>

25:23.520 --> 25:24.874
<i>Yeah</i>

25:25.000 --> 25:27.231
<i>I'm trying to forget your...</i>

